    "name": "There Is No Lore",
    "steam_appid": 3152430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时候你想坐下来享受一个美好、深刻、引人入胜的故事——但这里你得不到那个。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《毫无背景》确实是一款轻度roguelike<strong>卡组构建游戏</strong>——解锁卡牌，构建一层又一层的卡组！ 用你的卡组和饰品的配置智胜对手，观看它们赢得那些地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/0fe49803da4a67af5d3452cfd121f068.poster.avif?t=1766293527\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/0fe49803da4a67af5d3452cfd121f068.webm?t=1766293527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/0fe49803da4a67af5d3452cfd121f068.mp4?t=1766293527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩多种模式，从“故事”模式解锁一系列基础卡组，到草稿模式中从头创建自己的卡组。 在地图上规划你的路线，收集最好的卡牌，为最终的Boss战斗做好准备。不过要小心，一些棘手的战斗可能会挡路——为它们做好准备！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/6d5971fb4db74a9b857f07e2998d5791.poster.avif?t=1766293527\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/6d5971fb4db74a9b857f07e2998d5791.webm?t=1766293527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/6d5971fb4db74a9b857f07e2998d5791.mp4?t=1766293527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦你击败了特殊战斗，就拿走他们的一张卡牌。提前了解它们将有助于你规划你的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/700cc9bcf23a181d97e373f8fd1a2f47.poster.avif?t=1766293527\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/700cc9bcf23a181d97e373f8fd1a2f47.webm?t=1766293527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/700cc9bcf23a181d97e373f8fd1a2f47.mp4?t=1766293527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无限的组合和可能性在等待着你。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过90张卡牌，包含你期望的和你意想不到的效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过40个饰品，以不同方式影响你的卡组并排列你的策略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过20个地点供你游玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过20个初始卡组供你在游戏中构建。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过15个<strong>特殊战斗</strong>，从不同的角度挑战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不用有任何压力。尽情享受吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/880d12461699ecc2a76a5dd232c45b44.poster.avif?t=1766293527\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152430/extras/880d12461699ecc2a76a5dd232c45b44.webm?t=1766293527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
